va:valueAssertion.test: iaf:numeric-equal(iaf:abs(iaf:sum((iaf:sum($a), iaf:numeric-unary-minus((iaf:sum(($b, $c, iaf:sum($d), iaf:sum($e)))))))), iaf:sum(($f, iaf:numeric-unary-minus(iaf:sum($g)), iaf:numeric-unary-minus(iaf:sum($h)))))

pf:period.test: if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate else false()
